text: Ærest on eoccenforda.
Up &lang eoccenes to abbes dic.
Þet to cealdenwulle.
<../images/tbar.gif>to mearcforda &lang broces oð þene grenen weig.
Andlang weiges to broce<../images/tbar.gif>to wuduforda.
<../images/tbar.gif>adune be broce oð pippel riðiges ut scyte<../images/tbar.gif>þurhð dene mor a be riðige.
To guman graue.
<../images/tbar.gif>to pippel bricge<../images/tbar.gif>on þene sic æt þære fulan æc.
<../images/tbar.gif>to hæglea on þæne bradan mere.
<../images/tbar.gif>a be wyrt walan to bromcumbes heafod.
<../images/tbar.gif>on gerihtum to abbendune to þære port strete.
<../images/tbar.gif>andlang stret on hiwege<../images/tbar.gif>to ecgunes wyrðe.
Þenne on bacgan leah<../images/tbar.gif>on scæceling æcer.

<../images/tbar.gif>ut on stanford<../images/tbar.gif>to mægþeforda &lang lace ut on temese<../images/tbar.gif>on forð mid streame wið ufan micclanige on cearewyllan eft wið neoðan berige on temese<../images/tbar.gif>þer up be streame<../images/tbar.gif>on bacgan broc.
<../images/tbar.gif>on heafoces oran.
<../images/tbar.gif>on holan dene.
<../images/tbar.gif>on tidewaldes wylle.
Andlang broces ut on temese<../images/tbar.gif>forð mid streme oð geafling lace &lang lace.
Eft ut on temese<../images/tbar.gif>up be streame on occenes grestun dic.
Þet a be dic on eccen<../images/tbar.gif>þer up eft on eccen forda.
Æðeleaing uude colmanora.
And Geatescumbe hyren into ðys twentigum hidum.
Þa ic sylf studum gerad studum ge reow & rumoðlice gescarode me sylfum & minum foregengum & eftyrgengum to ecum rymete.
For Gode & for worulde.
Gif hwa þurh deofles lare ge nyrwe.
<../images/tbar.gif>ic Gode & sancta Marian meaglum mode on ece yrfe ge seald hæbbe.
Drihten his andweald genyðrige her & on ecnesse.
Nymþe he mid fulre dead bote geinnige<../images/tbar.gif>he on urum drihtne gereafoð.
